There are many cannabinoids that work differently for each individual. Make sure you smell it and it doesnt look "dry". Fuzzy and pungent in smell is usually my indicator. Be careful when asking a budtender. I find they are like diners and suggest meh product they're trying to get rid of.
If a good strain is grown poorly it wont be as good, so check top shelf quality "sativa" and "indica", trial and error. If you like a little indica in your sativa then a sativa "dominant" strain.
